nodes.notes:
ESPN sports — scores, standings, and schedules for NFL, NBA, NHL, EPL, F1, MLS.

Actions:
  scores — live and recent game results. Use when asked about scores, results, who won, who's playing.
  standings — season rankings and win-loss records. Use when asked about standings, rankings, league table, who's leading.
  schedule — upcoming games for a team. Use when asked about next game, upcoming matches, when does X play.

Rules:
- sport is required for every action.
- conference is ONLY for standings. Only NBA, NFL, and MLS have conferences. Values: east, west. Do NOT add conference unless the
user specifically asks for a conference.
- team is required for schedule (except F1).
- F1 results: use action "scores" (results maps to scores internally).

---schema
{
  "action": {
    "type": "string",
    "description": "One of: scores, standings, schedule",
    "required": true
  },
  "sport": {
    "type": "string",
    "required": true,
    "description": "Sport league. One of: nba, nfl, nhl, epl, mls, f1"
  },
  "team": {
    "type": "string",
    "description": "Team name or alias, e.g. lakers, seahawks, arsenal. For: schedule"
  },
  "conference": {
    "type": "string",
    "description": "Conference filter for NBA/NFL/MLS standings. One of: east, west. For: standings"
  }
}

